is underneath me.

32:15.668 --> 32:16.934
(ice cracking)

32:17.903 --> 32:20.237
See right down through there?

32:21.507 --> 32:24.508
This is all cracked to (bleep)
look at it.

32:28.580 --> 32:30.547
(ice cracking, popping)

32:32.551 --> 32:33.450
Oooh easy.

32:35.421 --> 32:37.120
(ice cracking)

32:40.459 --> 32:43.994
I gotta be (bleep)
to be doing this, eh.

32:45.364 --> 32:46.363
(ice cracking)

32:46.365 --> 32:48.365
You ask me what was going
through my head

32:48.367 --> 32:50.534
When I almost went through
the ice,

32:50.536 --> 32:52.602
I had one thing on my mind, b'y:

32:52.604 --> 32:55.138
To get the (bleep) out of there.

32:55.140 --> 32:56.974
(ice cracking)

32:56.976 --> 33:00.143
And I got pretty much the same
thing in my mind now.

33:00.145 --> 33:02.379
Listen to the (bleep) thing
cracking.

33:05.017 --> 33:05.515
(ice cracking)

